      <title>01-构词法</title>
      <link href="/posts/1cc74d01.html"/>
      <url>/posts/1cc74d01.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>通过一定的规则构成的新词, 叫做 “构词法” 。</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1. affixation  词缀法</span><br><span class="line">2. compounding 合成法</span><br><span class="line">3. conversion  转类法</span><br><span class="line">4. acronym     首字母缩略法</span><br><span class="line">5. clipping    截短法</span><br><span class="line">6. blending    拼缀法</span><br><span class="line">...</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>词缀法又叫派生法,即在一个单词前或后加上词缀,构成新的单词。分为”前缀法” 和 “后缀法”。</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">前缀 + 词根 + 后缀</span><br><span class="line">----------</span><br><span class="line">   含义----------</span><br><span class="line">          词性</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li>前缀法: 一般只引起意思上的变化而不造成词性的改变,只有少数能引起词类的变化。</li><li>后缀法: 一般只引起词性上的变化而不造成意思的变化。</li></ol><h3 id="变名词的后缀"><a href="#变名词的后缀" class="headerlink" title="变名词的后缀"></a>变名词的后缀</h3><table><thead><tr><th align="left">-ence, -ance</th><th align="left">-tion, -sion</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="left">存在 exist-existence</td><td align="left">生产 produce-production</td></tr><tr><td align="left">发生 occur-occurrence</td><td align="left">介绍 introduce-introduction</td></tr><tr><td align="left">查阅&#x2F;参考 refer-reference</td><td align="left">消费 consume-consumption</td></tr><tr><td align="left">更喜欢&#x2F;偏好 prefer-preference</td><td align="left">减少 reduce-reduction</td></tr><tr><td align="left">不同 differ-difference</td><td align="left">认为&#x2F;假想 assume-assumption</td></tr><tr><td align="left">接受 accept-acceptance</td><td align="left">毁灭 destroy-destruction</td></tr><tr><td align="left">出现&#x2F;外表 appear-appearance</td><td align="left">描写 describe-description</td></tr><tr><td align="left">履行 perform-performance</td><td align="left">打断 interrupt-interruption</td></tr><tr><td align="left">抵制 resist-resistance</td><td align="left">采纳&#x2F;收养 adopt-adoption</td></tr><tr><td align="left">指导 guide-guidance</td><td align="left">防止 prevent-prevention</td></tr></tbody></table><table><thead><tr><th align="left">-ment</th><th align="left">-ness</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="left">广告 advertise-advertisement</td><td align="left">意识 aware-awareness</td></tr><tr><td align="left">同意 agree-agreement</td><td align="left">苦 bitter-bitterness</td></tr><tr><td align="left">惊奇 amaze-amazement</td><td align="left">盲目 blind-blindness</td></tr><tr><td align="left">吃惊 astonish-astonishment</td><td align="left">冷静 calm-calmness</td></tr><tr><td align="left">通告 announce-announcement</td><td align="left">聪明 clever-cleverness</td></tr><tr><td align="left">安排 arrange-arrangement</td><td align="left">疯狂 crazy-craziness</td></tr><tr><td align="left">评估 assess-assessment</td><td align="left">渴望 eager-eagerness</td></tr><tr><td align="left">发展 develop-development</td><td align="left">公平 fair-fairness</td></tr><tr><td align="left">失望 disappoint-disappointment</td><td align="left">愚蠢 foolish-foolishness</td></tr><tr><td align="left">雇佣,就业 employ-employment</td><td align="left">适合 fit-fitness</td></tr></tbody></table>]]></content>
      
      
      
